<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>居住房屋租赁合同</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8"></meta>
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no"></meta>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=2.5, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes"></meta>
<style>
body{
	font-size:12px;
	font-family:microsoft yahei, trebuchet ms, tahoma, sans-serif;
	margin:0 6px;
	color:#333;
}
.hp{ 
	overflow:hidden;
}
h1{
	text-align:center;
	font-size:1.8em;
	margin:1.5em 0 .8em;
}
h2,h3{
	font-size:1.17em;
	margin:1em 0 .35em;
}
h1,h2,h3{
	color:#000;
}
p{
	margin:2px 0;
	line-height:1.5em;
	text-align:justify;
}
img{
	display:inline-block;
	max-width:100%;
}
p label{
	float:left;
	display:inline-block;
	width:50px;
}
.img-wrapper{
	margin-left:60px;
	display:block;
}
.img-list-wrapper{
	overflow:hidden;
}
.img-list-wrapper img{
	width:100px;
	float:left;
	display:inline-block;
}
.img-list-wrapper img + img{
	margin-left:5px;
}
.fl{
	float:left;
}
label.lg{
	width:135px;
}
.banner{
	margin:8px 0;
}
.title-terms{
	font-size: 1.5em;
    margin: 2em 0 .8em;
}
.remarks{
	margin:10px 0;
}
.remarks strong{
	font-size:1.2em;
}
table{
	border-collapse:collapse;
	width:100%;
	margin-top:10px;
	margin-bottom:4px;
}
table td{
	border-top:1px dashed #ddd;
	border-bottom:1px dashed #ddd;
}
table th,
table td{
	line-height:22px;
	text-align:left;
	width:25%;
}
</style>	
</head>
<body>
	<h1>居住房屋租赁合同</h1>
	<div class="banner">
		<p><strong>甲方（出租人）：</strong>${landlordName}</p>
		<p><strong>乙方（承租人）：</strong>${renterRealName}</p>
	</div>
	<p>该租约内容是由房东添加并经过您的确认，具有等同于您和房东线下签约合同一样的合约效应，并作为您使用蘑菇租房平台系统相关功能的凭证，若对合约内容有疑问，请与房东联系沟通。</p>
	
	<h2>租金及支付方式</h2>
	<p><label class="lg">租赁起止日期</label>：${startAndEndTime}</p>
	<p><label class="lg">租赁期限</label>：${leaseTerm} </p>
	<p><label class="lg">租金付款方式</label>：${rentPayType}</p>
	<p><label class="lg">每月租金金额</label>：${money}元</p>
	<p><label class="lg">人民币（大写）</label>：${moneyRMB}</p>
	<p><label class="lg">押金金额</label>：${depositMoney}元（${depositListStr}）</p>
	<p><label class="lg">人民币（大写）</label>：${depositMoneyRMB}</p>
	<p><label class="lg">首期款</label>：${firstTermAmount}元（${firstListStr}）</p> 
	<p><label class="lg">人民币（大写）</label>：${firstTermAmountRMB}</p> 
	<p><label class="lg">每期租金金额</label>：${rentMoney}</p>
	<p><label class="lg">人民币（大写）</label>：${rentMoneyRMB}</p>
	
	<h2>入住人身份信息</h2>
	<p><label>姓名</label>：${realName}</p>
	<p><label>性别</label>：${sex}</p>
	<p><label>联系电话</label>：${cellphone}</p>
	
	<h2>房源信息</h2>
	<p><label>房源地址</label>：${roomInfo}</p>
	<p><label>建筑面积</label>：${area}平方米</p>
	
	<h2>线下合同照片</h2>
	<p class="hp"><span class="img-wrapper img-list-wrapper">${offlineContractPhoto}</span></p>
		
	<h2>其它</h2>
	<p class="remarks"><strong>备注：<u>${contractRemark}</u></strong></p>
		
</body>
</html>
